    <title>用 hexo 搭建个人博客</title>
    <link href="/2026/02/21/%E7%94%A8%20hexo%20%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/"/>
    <url>/2026/02/21/%E7%94%A8%20hexo%20%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="准备">准备</h1><ul><li>Node.js</li><li>Git</li><li>gihub 账号</li></ul><h1 id="配置-ssh">配置 SSH</h1><ol><li><p>运行 <code>ssh-keygen -t rsa -C &quot;Github 注册的邮箱地址&quot;</code></p></li><li><p>不停回车或肯定，直到出现一个奇怪图案。</p></li><li><p>复制 <code>~\.ssh\id_rsa.pub</code> 文件里面的所有内容。</p></li><li><p>登录到 github，点击右上角头像-&gt;“Settings”-&gt;“SSH and GPG keys”-&gt;“New SSH key”。</p></li><li><p>“Title” 随便写，在”Key“里粘贴你之前复制的内容。</p></li><li><p>点击“Add SSH Key”。</p></li><li><p>终端输入 <code>ssh -T git@github.com</code>，出现“Hi…”的信息就大功告成了。</p></li></ol><h1 id="搭建博客环境">搭建博客环境</h1><p>准备一个目录。在目录下执行</p><figure class="highlight mipsasm"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs mipsasm">npm <span class="hljs-keyword">install </span>hexo-cli -g  <br>hexo init <span class="hljs-keyword">blog </span> <br>cd <span class="hljs-keyword">blog </span> <br>npm <span class="hljs-keyword">install </span> <br>hexo s<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>出现 <code>localhost:4000</code> 就表示成功了。浏览器打开此网址，即可预览自己的博客，默认有一个 Hello World。<code>Ctrl+C</code> 停止本地博客。</p><h1 id="部署">部署</h1><h2 id="创建-github-仓库">创建 github 仓库</h2><ol><li><p>进入 github，点击右上角“+”-&gt;“New repository”。</p></li><li><p>“Repository name”写 <code>你的用户名.github.io</code>。</p></li><li><p>“Add README”选择“On”。</p></li><li><p>其他选项不用改，点击“Create repository”。</p></li></ol><h2 id="部署网站">部署网站</h2><p>打开刚刚创建的仓库，点击右上方绿色的 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mpadded width="+6pt" height="+6pt" lspace="3pt" voffset="3pt" mathbackground="green"><mstyle mathcolor="white"><mtext>&lt;&gt; Code</mtext></mstyle></mpadded></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\colorbox{green}{\textcolor{white}{&lt;&gt; Code}}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1.3335em;vertical-align:-0.3391em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.9944em;"><span style="top:-2.9944em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3.3335em;"></span><span class="stretchy colorbox" style="height:1.3335em;background-color:green;"></span></span><span style="top:-3.3335em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3.3335em;"></span><span class="mord boxpad"><span class="mord" style="color:white;">&lt;&gt; Code</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3391em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> 按钮，“Clone”处选择“SSH”，复制下方的地址。</p><p>接着进入博客目录，打开 <code>_config.yml</code>，翻到最底下，把 <code>deploy</code> 一段改成</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-attr">deploy:</span>  <br>  <span class="hljs-attr">type:</span> <span class="hljs-string">git</span>  <br>  <span class="hljs-attr">repository:</span> <span class="hljs-string">粘贴你刚刚复制的地址（如</span> <span class="hljs-string">git@github.com:xtttai2/xtttai2.github.io.git）</span>  <br>  <span class="hljs-attr">branch:</span> <span class="hljs-string">main</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后在目录下运行</p><figure class="highlight ada"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs ada">npm install hexo-deployer-git <span class="hljs-comment">--save</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>最后运行</p><figure class="highlight sas"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sas">hexo cl <span class="hljs-variable">&amp;&amp;</span> hexo g <span class="hljs-variable">&amp;&amp;</span> hexo d<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>此时再去仓库看看就会发现除了 <code>README.md</code> 还多出了许多东西。</p><p>等待几分钟，访问 <code>你的用户名.github.io</code>，就可以看到你的博客了（默认只有一个 Hello World）。</p><h1 id="基本操作">基本操作</h1><h2 id="新建文章">新建文章</h2><figure class="highlight livecodeserver"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs livecodeserver">hexo <span class="hljs-built_in">new</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">post</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;文章标题&quot;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="Front-matter">Front-matter</h2><p>开头的代码块，支持 YAML 与 JSON 格式。比如</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-meta">---  </span><br><span class="hljs-attr">title:</span> <span class="hljs-string">Hello</span> <span class="hljs-string">World</span>  <br><span class="hljs-attr">date:</span> <span class="hljs-number">2013</span><span class="hljs-string">/7/13</span> <span class="hljs-number">20</span><span class="hljs-string">:46:25</span>  <br><span class="hljs-meta">---</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>常用设置见下表：</p><table><thead><tr><th>设置</th><th>描述</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>title</td><td>标题</td></tr><tr><td>date</td><td>建立日期</td></tr><tr><td>updated</td><td>更新日期</td></tr><tr><td>tags</td><td>标签</td></tr><tr><td>categories</td><td>类别</td></tr></tbody></table><p>剩下的可以自己玩了。</p>]]></content>
    
    
